text: Rock of the Westies is the tenth studio album by Elton John and was released on 20 October 1975. It topped the album charts in Canada and the United States. It went to the top 10 in Australia, Denmark, New Zealand, Norway, Spain, Sweden and the United Kingdom. == Track listing == * Sides one and two were combined as tracks 1â€“9 on CD reissues. == References == Category:1975 albums Category:Elton John albums
